author: Engineezy
description:
In today's stream, I’m diving back into Factorio, and this time… I’m tearing my entire factory apart to rebuild it from scratch.

Will my engineering brain actually help me make things better — or just create a bigger mess? Come hang out, watch the chaos unfold, and maybe help me figure out how to stop everything from catching fire.

If you want to troll me and make my shop counter explode, head over to this link:
www.engineezy.com

title: Rebuilding My Entire Factorio Factory From Scratch | Engineezy Live ep.3
